{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778377847724,"sessionID":"ses_1f073153bffeZIBd6V2lk1nCBt","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"apply_patch","callID":"call_fxhY6PZdFGJbUA69mnwdtawA","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"patchText":"*** Begin Patch\n*** Add File: /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/DESIGN_PATTERNS.md\n+# Design Pattern Notes for Issue #31981\n+\n+## Term Reviewed\n+\n+- `GO:0072318` clathrin coat disassembly\n+- Requested process context: `GO:0072583` clathrin-dependent endocytosis\n+\n+## Relevant Pattern\n+\n+The existing logical definition for `GO:0072318` conforms to `src/design_patterns/cc_disassembly.yaml`:\n+\n+- Genus: `GO:0022411` cellular component disassembly\n+- Differentia: `results_in_disassembly_of` some `GO:0030118` clathrin coat\n+\n+The request is to place this disassembly process in the broader biological process in which it occurs. This should be represented as a necessary `part_of` relationship rather than an additional `intersection_of` axiom, because clathrin coat disassembly is not defined solely as any cellular component disassembly that is part of clathrin-dependent endocytosis.\n+\n+## Decision\n+\n+Add:\n+\n+```obo\n+relationship: part_of GO:0072583 ! clathrin-dependent endocytosis\n+```\n+\n+No change to the existing logical definition is needed.\n*** End Patch"},"output":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA DESIGN_PATTERNS.md","metadata":{"diff":"Index: /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/DESIGN_PATTERNS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/DESIGN_PATTERNS.md\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/DESIGN_PATTERNS.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,25 @@\n+# Design Pattern Notes for Issue #31981\n+\n+## Term Reviewed\n+\n+- `GO:0072318` clathrin coat disassembly\n+- Requested process context: `GO:0072583` clathrin-dependent endocytosis\n+\n+## Relevant Pattern\n+\n+The existing logical definition for `GO:0072318` conforms to `src/design_patterns/